// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/dtSBzc kisquadrille, written 2023 by jt

// kisquadrille aka tetrakis square tiling https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tetrakis_square_tiling
// Basically a checker xored with a diagonal checker.
// Could also be described as alternating sand-clock (sandglass / hourglass) pattern.

// Related: https://www.shadertoy.com/view/cl2BzV kisrhombille tiling.

// tags: square, checker, pattern, tiling, euclidean, tesselation, diagonal, tetrakis, kisquadrille

